A python SDL warpper and example code, sdl.py and smpeg.py are generate by ctypesgen.
It should be:
	NO segmentation fault
	NO memory leak
	NO double free
	Stable and acceptable performance

Passed test on rhel and winxp, all function work.
rhel need build SDL_ttf 2.0.10+ and smpeg byself.
winxp need find and download dll (
SDL_gfx.dll maybe need search or build byself,
libstdc++-6.dll and libgcc_s_dw2-1.dll are provide by mingw ).

require: SDL_image, SDL_mixer, SDL_gfx, SDL_ttf, smpeg
provide: basic image and text widget, music and movie support.

files detail:
example:
	main.py, define.py, ...
core:
	core/
	It also can use be an example how to run sdl with python
resource:
	data/
	You *need* create data/ and
	put img.png, msgothic.ttc, noise.wav, test.mpg
	under this directory before run example

example keyboard shortcut:
	esc: exit
	s, d: play, stop movie
	q, w: play, stop music
	z: list music and movie info
	arrow keys: move image

how to use:
	You need look example,
	it didn't have any reference or tutorial in this time ...

